reviewText: I AM IN THE PROCESS OF REPLACING MY COLLECTION OF VHS TAPES WITH DVD'S. I HAVE WELL OVER 10.000 MOVIES IN MY COLLECTION. THEREFORE I AM ORDERING THESE FROM AMAZON. HAVING A MOVIE SET LIKE SAM ELLOTT TRIPLE SAVES ME BOTH TIME AND MONEY. I WAS VERY SATISFIED WITH THIS PRODUCT. THE PRICE WAS RIGHT,THE PRODUCT ARRIVED ON TIME AND THE ART WORK AND COVER WAS IN MENT CONDITION. THE MOVIES PLAYED WITHOUT A HITCH. I WAS VERY HAPPY, KEEP UP THE GOOD WORK. I'LL BE ORDERING MANY, MANY MORE DVD'S.
